issue.body:
We need to move from class based approach for `Feature`s to instance based.

Right now features are still setup for evaluation (#289) this makes no sense with the rest of the codebase at this point. We must clean this up.

Other than that we also need to make `Feature` a dataclass or namedtuple or something. The point here being that `.name()` should just be `.name` and `.NAME` shouldn't exist anymore (same for dtype).
